sun.jvm.hotspot.debugger.cdbg.basic

Interface ResolveListener


  • public interface ResolveListener
    Provides notification about failed resolutions in the debug info database without causing the entire resolve operation to fail

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void resolveFailed(Sym containingSymbol, LazyBlockSym failedResolve, java.lang.String detail)
      Indicates failure to resolve reference from one symbol to another (currently occurs only from BlockSyms to other BlockSyms)
      void resolveFailed(Sym containingSymbol, LazyType failedResolve, java.lang.String detail)
      Indicates failure to resolve reference to a type from a symbol
      void resolveFailed(Type containingType, LazyType failedResolve, java.lang.String detail)
      Indicates failure to resolve a type within another type
      void resolveFailed(Type containingType, java.lang.String staticFieldName)
      Indicates failure to resolve the address of a static field in a type
